{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water and sugar in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and weigh in peaches. Heat <b>10 min\/100°C\/speed 4<b>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and set aside.","Add mint and teabags to mixing bowl, then allow mixture to infuse for 5 minutes. Strain tea into a jug through simmering basket. Return mixture to mixing bowl and allow to cool (approx. 2 hours). Discard contents of simmering basket.","Once tea mixture is cool, add ice cubes, vodka and limes then mix <b>10 sec\/speed 2<b>. Insert simmering basket, hold in place with spatula, then strain into a jug.","Serve in 8 glasses with extra ice cubes, topped up with lemonade and garnished with fresh mint leaves."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1000 g water","100 g sugar","2 peaches, quartered (approx. 200 g)","15 g fresh mint leaves, plus extra for serving","2 teabags, black tea","200 g ice cubes, plus extra for serving","300 g vodka","2 limes, quartered","300 g lemonade, or to taste"]}],"id":"r104314","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-j2WDWbTbggI\/XZXZB3S3dWI\/AAAAAAAAgEM\/yfuCrOAmoQ0rSCHx9vCJ9x67hLrrXV_OwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Y3sz251wHvnRaRa9.png","title":"Boozy Peach and Mint Iced Tea","publishedAt":"2016-07-25T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"0.1 g","fat":"0 g","uom":"per 1 glass","carbohydrates":"15.8 g","calories":"615 kJ \/ 147 kcal"},"usefulItems":"jug, glasses, refrigerator","basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h 25m","8 glasses"]}